{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "But we marched up all the way to the camp, in the hope that being a new camp, so we should be disinfected.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "We'll get a shower.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And probably we'll get a hot cabbage soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Which was, everybody was starving after a hot soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "It doesn't matter if there's nothing in it, just hot, something hot into our stomach.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "So we try to get up as fast as we can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "But the trouble is another transport arrived just before us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And there were already about 10,000 people jammed in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And when we came in, they jammed us in too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And before we could get any food, according to the German rules, you have to be clean.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "You have to be [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "You had to be uniform down, shower with soap, and new uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "And there's only one shower section with six shower heads.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "So they could only let in about 10 or 12 people at a time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And there were thousands of people in front of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "So we got no-- no hot soup on that they, and all night standing in the snow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "On the mountaintop in Austria, in the middle of winter in January, it's very cold and windy, as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "So people sat down, froze to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "Be it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "My friends, my delirious friends, who said, mother, mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "I'm coming to you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "Come to me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And I said, look, if you lie down like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "He was already delirious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "And he says, Frank, here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "Take this piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "I was saving it all the last four days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "But you can have it now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "I-- I don't need it anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "I hope I freeze to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "He did.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
